This code should not be copied or used for any school projects or used in any professional programs since it is intended
to be a learning testbed and most likely is in some state of broken or incomplete in fucntionality. Use at your own risk.

This program was outlined by Bart Massey for an internetworking protocols class and has been modified by Kevin Riedl.
The initial intent was to be an assignment, but this is an ongoing project to teach myself (Kevin Riedl) how basic
packets are passed from device to device.
